Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So close...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Any moment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chunin Exam...the Forest of Death...\Nthree years have passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You want our "Earth Scroll," don't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:01:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, let's begin...\N{\i1}the struggle for the scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll put our lives on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Genin who once feared\Nyour menacing air
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,has now matured, hasn't he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The young Sharingan that child turned\Nat me had a fine look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's able to use the Sharingan to that\N extent as his age, he gets a passing grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, with training, he can become\Nan outstanding gem, superior to Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is what convinced me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to the trauma\Nhe carries with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke would seek me out for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you gave him\Na Curse Mark and also took steps
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep watch over the Chunin Exam\Nto see how he reacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Anko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...I was planning to threaten\Nthe Leaf, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If his Chakra was completely sucked out\Nby Yoroi's powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke would be forced to use\Nthe power of the Curse Mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now release it.\N{\i1}That sweet power of yours...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dancing Leaf Shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not going...to let this thing...\N{\i1}swallow me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lions Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What more can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The will to brush off the effects\Nof the Curse Mark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way he made use of the Sharingan\Nin a desperate situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Actual battle does indeed make\NNinja mature greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the right decision to make him\Ncontinue with the Chunin Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He did well to improve that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent... He did well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no reason to keep him with\Nthe Leaf Ninja any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one who can train him better\Nthan I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No one other than me, who can understand\Nthe darkness in his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as paint him in your colors,\NLord Orochimaru...isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though the destruction of\Nthe Hidden Leaf Village was an afterthought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for me to prepare\Nthe next medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you will be able to go through\Nthe Reanimation Jutsu in perfect condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will give you a punishment\N{\i1}that is appropriate for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who has become intoxicated by Jutsu\N{\i1}and allowed it to go to your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will take all of your Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My arms can't move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn geezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that,\Nmy Jutsu was taken from me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the time of my reanimation\Nwas postponed. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All preparations are complete...\Nand the plan is in its final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The unexpected accident is\Nnow but a trivial price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, your body will become mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything I do is for my goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I do it to clear away the darkness\N{\i1}that stands in the way of my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Kabuto...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Lord Orochimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...\NThat body will be mine shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be reanimated soon.\NI feel great...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've reached your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In your condition, if I don't administer\Na rank 10 medication, your body will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I will change medications.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It will just take a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That menacing air... But his body\N{\i1}should already have passed its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he hangs on by his sheer will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I cannot leave\NLord Orochimaru's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hokage... When you defeated\Nboth giant heads of Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:09:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you were just one step away from\Ndestruction of the Hidden Leaf Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary Sannin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were fighting Tsunade\Nand Jiraiya at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You never looked so menacing...\Nso full of ambition, even then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fearful of how much you've grown,\NLord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If all goes well, not only the Five Kage,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but the entire continent will bow down\Nbefore you, Lord Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When you obtain Sasuke's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidori Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The report is reliable?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. According to the squad sent\Nto check that lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Anbu Black Ops stationed there to do surveillance\N had disappeared along with the Three-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone who could handle the Three-Tails\N{\i1}in the short time since we lost contact...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cost of reanimation is this pain.\N{\i1}But it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nothing compared to the greatness\N{\i1}that I am gaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The nature of this Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, I've never seen\N{\i1}this Change in Chakra Form before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You came...just as I thought you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing more to learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even here before you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can become heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You didn't kill all of them...\N{\i1}How naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are others I'd rather kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unless you become heartless,\N{\i1}you will never defeat Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I stand before him, I'll be heartless,\N{\i1}whether I want to be or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru, you are weaker than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no longer any need for me\Nto give you my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some nerve...\Nyou're still an Uchiha fledgling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't been a fledgling,\Nyou would've had no chance at me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,were eyeing me,\Ntrying to appraise this "fledgling"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the forest\Nduring the Chunin Exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire Style: Dragon Flame Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you...after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you put dibs on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you had me bound to you\Nwith this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you come,\N{\i1}Lord Orochimaru will give you power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Are you coming?\N{\i1}- Or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this weak guy keeps dawdling,\N{\i1}I'm going to want to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just try to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not the only one\N{\i1}Lord Orochimaru favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're bound to Lord Orochimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in exchange for gaining powers\N{\i1}via the Curse Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We no longer have any freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To gain something,\N{\i1}we have to give something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it you're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't forget your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ready to give my body if it meant\NI could attain my goal of revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wanted a Sharingan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi didn't work out...\NThat's why you came after me, a fledgling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?\NYou who they called the Genius Sannin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you turned out to be what they call\Non the streets, "just an ordinary prodigy."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't even live up to\Nthe Uchiha name, much less surpass it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the best prodigy is only ordinary\Nagainst the Uchiha name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,disgustingly trying to approach\Nthe powers of the Uchiha
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,by drowning yourself in drugs and\Ntrying to overcome your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems so shameless and comical to me,\Nwho possesses that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's more,\NI don't like the way you do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You hopped from hideout to hideout,\Nconducting experiments...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Toying with life after life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying you were trying to\Nunravel the order of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:18:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You continued to toy with others for\Nyour own stupid and selfish reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why... Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To measure my own abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Measure your own abilities...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that the only reason...\N{\i1}you killed everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake with white scales...\Nso that is your true form...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You conducted experiment after experiment\N so that you could move from body to body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's how you ended up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:19:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Sasuke...\NGive me your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake that slithers on the ground\Ncan only dream of flying through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted it so badly that\Nyou went after the fledgling in the nest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you became targeted\Nas the prey instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By the eyes of a hawk\Nsoaring high above in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
